{"tid":726565,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] Lanota 集中討論區","createTime":"2018-07-02T13:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T11:35:26.000Z","uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b557be13f54b2bea21613b0fbec3cbb6aa153c2b","tid":726565,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36279765_2244599685556513_2463074752533626880_o.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=a29a07a8d0dd7341f2b4ceb9c52b583e&amp;oe=5BE838F7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36279765_2244599685556513_2463074752533626880_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3Da29a07a8d0dd7341f2b4ceb9c52b583e%26oe%3D5BE838F7&h=a8f0bb3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36330918_2246148818734933_877015038894800896_o.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=ee7185db340eaa46bba7f580bf77b3de&amp;oe=5BB181E7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36330918_2246148818734933_877015038894800896_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3Dee7185db340eaa46bba7f580bf77b3de%26oe%3D5BB181E7&h=a8c10d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 咩係Lanota?<br />\nA: Lanota係由Noxy Games推出嘅繪本風RPG節拍game，可謂繼Rayark出嘅節拍遊戲後嘅另一台產佳作！<br />\n<br />\nQ: 背景故事大約講咩?<br />\nA: 在250年前，世界因為「靜默化」的災難而使得大部分的場所皆失去了聲音與色彩。只有使用前人創造出的一種能源濃縮體─「音礦」，才能讓這些場所恢復原狀。只不過以現在的技術，已經無法再次製造出這個人工物質。為了要一=邊確保世界的正常運作並將受到災害影響的地方恢復原狀，唯一手段便是再利用過去的人們遺留下的音礦。<br />\n<br />\n本遊戲將由玩家扮演主角菲希卡與里莫，兩人帶著所擁有的「音礦調律裝置」，將各個場所不可利用的「無序」音礦，「調律」至可正常運作的「有序」狀態，進而恢復世界的聲音與色彩。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解玩Lanota?<br />\nA: Lanota嘅原型係嚟自機舖嘅Maimai，但佢打破咗physical嘅限制，令圓盤可以旋轉、平移、瞬移等，再搭配創新嘅譜面，拉、打、撳同上下移，玩法可以話係千變萬化。獨特嘅世界觀、繪本風加上BGM嘅烘托，帶出fantasy、hopeless但有一絲曙光嘅氣氛，令玩家可以全程投入Lanota嘅世界。搭配不同風格但同樣動人嘅歌曲， 集Cytus嘅創新同Deemo嘅故事性一身！每個chapter都有精心設計嘅魔王曲配以精緻嘅動畫，挑戰你感官嘅極限！價錢十分實惠只需$15，當然入面有side story買。如果玩悶咗story mode，佢仲有啲擴充包係即打嘅譜面，不過得一個chapter，其他就要買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係一啲遊戲片段:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhTKyRGNLMo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhTKyRGNLMo&d=RmGgjlo2L4VoqaZYwsVXVxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=f7ecb5c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhTKyRGNLMo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Q5qvmu9bww&amp;t=8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9Q5qvmu9bww%26t%3D8s&d=RmGgjlo2L4VoqaZYwsVXVxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=5b55f7b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Q5qvmu9bww&amp;t=8s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgVrChoF52Y&amp;t=24s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKgVrChoF52Y%26t%3D24s&d=RmGgjlo2L4VoqaZYwsVXVxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=4af5197a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgVrChoF52Y&amp;t=24s</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook Page:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lanota/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flanota%2F&d=RmGgjlo2L4VoqaZYwsVXVxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=93b0ebaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lanota/</a>"},{"pid":"1de646facf7a332de0d1c9833cef9ddbaef1760e","tid":726565,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f5cc96f9f340c8cc506ee65ecc9b9f50d3b37e","tid":726565,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf90e003e571397c02f1149679d7f6b4ea96bd5","tid":726565,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b259f1bc303